Four most important behavioural variables were identified through the survey data, namely 1) How I feel that I manage my different roles; 2) How much effort I spend on it; 3) When I think about my different roles and 4) Where I think about them. The four variables helped us find behavioural patterns among the participants(see the figure below), and three personas were created based on it.\
